 impossible to move it.\r\n\r\nIf I remember well, this used to work some months ago, so I think it was broken recently.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open gzclient</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Insert any light from the toolbar</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select the new light on the world tree - a bounding box appears around the light</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Choose translate / rotate mode - the manipulator handles show up attached to the light, but trying to drag them deselects the light, making it impossible to move it.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>If I remember well, this used to work some months ago, so I think it was broken recently.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-12-09T12:22:49.253643+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:43:47.634393+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1384}